column2: Janet Marylyn Frager’s son is actor Christopher Lloyd (full name: Christopher Allen Lloyd), best known for roles such as Dr. Emmett “Doc” Brown in the *Back to the Future* films and Reverend Jim Ignatowski on *Taxi*.
